title: Sports Authority Store Locations
name: Sports Authority Store Locations
description:
This dataset displays the location of 421 Sports authority retail stores throughout the United States. This data was collected from the Sports Authority webpage and store locater at: http://www.sportsauthority.com/home/index.jsp?clickid=topnav_home_img
This data was geocoded according to the address provided in order to obtain the latitude and longitude coordinates for each of the stores. This data was accessed on December 13, 2007.

properties.Center0: Great Mall of the Bay Area
